  mock hold-out - it returned MockData.profiles (minus already-swiped ids)
  instead of querying the live `profiles` table. Every other profile path
  (me/byId/likedYou/matches) had already been moved to the real tables; this
  one was left on mock because "server-side discovery/ranking isn't built."
